  "title": "Project Engineer (Construction)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Manage projects and programs, overseeing manpower supervision.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the Project Manager to implement necessary actions based on inspection reports, ensuring clear and accurate execution.</li>\n  <li>Maintain a log of inspections, actions taken, and re-inspections to track rectified non-conformities.</li>\n  <li>Submit shop drawings and material samples for review, ensuring they meet project specifications.</li>\n  <li>Assist the Project Manager in planning and allocating labour, materials, plant, transport, and equipment.</li>\n  <li>Organize the activities of Site Supervisors and their workforce, aligning with project requirements.</li>\n  <li>Monitor health and safety protocols on projects to ensure compliance with local regulations and safe working practices.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that projects stay within the budget for labour and materials as outlined by the Project Manager.</li>\n  <li>Inspect site progress and productivity, documenting and submitting progress claims for certification and payment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
